#TBT to my first charity show where I got taken off stage in 2012. I drove in Hurricane Sandy to do this show. Every time someone asks me to do a charity show I say “I don’t think I’m right for this.” This charity specifically said they loved my “real” jokes. 

Imagine being Boston’s First Lady,  Angela Menino and getting upset about a “morning after pill” joke while your husband, who was mayor, was pushing for kids to get abortions without the consent of their parents. 

I would have loved to perform for the woman at the shelter who would have had a great time. Instead I got to upset “fancy ladies in expensive shoes” Imagine calling yourself a fancy lady and not throwing up in your mouth? 

All this to say, I’m on tour. Come out and get your feelings hurt. Link in bio. 

#Boston #BostonHerald #charity #fun #comedy #angelamenino #lol #politicans #hypocrites
